Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Encounters are mysterious!\NBut Osaka is even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is a 60-minute Naniwa special
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,filled with incidents and mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I spun the roulette of destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and always watched you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is it that I'm this happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,yet I feel sad when I look at the horizon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as if I'm looking at\Nmyself back then, from afar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spin the roulette of destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thinking too hard about\Nthis and that is a mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? The person of\Nyour destiny is right there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,watching you always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.81,0:01:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the incident in Toyonaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is last week's incident in Harakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no witnesses to these killings,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and they're dozens of kilometers away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're checking into how\Nthese two victims are connected,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but they still share nothing in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Chief Detective Toyama\NOsaka Police Headquarters"\Nbut they still share nothing in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Chief Detective Toyama\NOsaka Police Headquarters"\NThere's only one thing: The knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing: The knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but they\Nwere both stabbed in the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,through their wallets in their jackets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you told the media about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not the wallet part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the second killing\Nwasn't some moron's copycat attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct. It was definitely the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serial murders...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the murders are at\Nrandom, it'll cause a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toyama. You'd best be extra careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Hattori Heizo\NOsaka Chief of Police"\NToyama. You'd best be extra careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Hattori Heizo\NOsaka Chief of Police"\NYes. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Naniwa Serial Murder Case"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the Tennoji Zoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the Osaka Dome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is the Tsutenkaku Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whadya think? Osaka's nice, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! This is a great view!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dunno, it's no different\Nfrom the Tokyo Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be dumb! Don't compare\Nthis with that tasteless red thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Tsutenkaku and the new world all around it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are brimming with the Osakans' humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost like downtown Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about some food now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer!\NI'm waiting for someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine. Guess I'll have a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me why you called me to Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're concerned about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have another real reason, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no! There's really no work this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just thought I'd show\Nyou guys around Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no telling when you'll die, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a bad dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Dream?\N- Yeah. It happens when we catch a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he winds up stabbing\Nand killing you instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! Don't kill people on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you have it. So just enjoy Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! He's finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Sakata Yusuke (26)\NTojiri Police Detective, Section 1"\NOh! He's finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Sakata Yusuke (26)\NTojiri Police Detective, Section 1"\NI'm Sakata of the Osaka Police, Tojiri Station!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Sakata Yusuke (26)\NTojiri Police Detective, Section 1"\NSorry for being so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is a police detective here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My old man said that if\NMori-han's coming to Osaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he should have a proper tour guide!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where is my old man?\NHe said he was going to stop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chief is busy in a\Nmeeting about the incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The incidents"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, did you get the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did just like you asked and\Nborrowed the Tojiri station's best one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, now. Don't tell me this car is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the best?! Cop cars are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can pass other cars even in traffic jams!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, where would you like to go, guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you making us tour Osaka in this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You don't like it? It's brand new!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Should I turn on the siren?\NWe can go even faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what he means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It feels like we're being arrested,\Nso it's kind of embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about that!\NYou haven't done anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold your heads high!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whadya think?! This is real udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The soup's so clear you can see the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a light flavor, but good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tastes like nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Heiji! Who's she? A new girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it seem that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! I'm just a regular Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suddenly got a chill...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, where to next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm, the next thing Osaka is famous for is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This takoyaki is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never had ones with such big octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:07:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing. It just feels like\Nsomeone's been watching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about it and eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't take my eyes off you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you were on a diet, Ran-neechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okonomiyaki? Why didn't you\Nsay so before the takoyaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already passed a great place I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going the wrong way!\NWe can't get there on Midosuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Osaka is full of one-way roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so you often have to go way out of your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, shall I show\Nthem a nearby place I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing this place was nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna call my mom real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister! Don't forget the rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:47.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You eat okonomiyaki with rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! It's a main dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rice with the sauce on it is great, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Osaka's neat!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! That seat is taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Kudo, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji's always talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} does?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.\NI already know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're the Kudo broad\Nfrom Tokyo who's seducing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, I think you have the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have just one thing to say to you:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji and I were once\Nbound by "chains of iron"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to mess with Heiji,\Nyou gotta go through me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "Kudo" I talked about is a guy! A guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Toyama Kazuha (17) Heiji's childhood friend"\NThe "Kudo" I talked about is a guy! A guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "Kudo" I talked about is a guy! A guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this girl is Kudo's squeeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Squeeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-It isn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- She says she isn't.\N- She's just embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you ask Kudo to come too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! Kudo's sitting right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-He couldn't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, tell us more about\Nthis "chains of iron" thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we were kids, we found my\Nold man's handcuffs in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we got stuck together when\NI pretended to be a policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was lame; we found ourselves in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was not lame! We had to bathe\Nand use the bathroom together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You moron! Don't tell them that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bathe and use the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a smelly relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To commemorate it, I put a piece\Nof the chain in here for good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gross! Throw that thing away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say! Are you two going out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no! Heiji and I are just childhood friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm like his big sister who's\Nalways looking after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her dad's chief detective of the\NOsaka police and my dad's friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we've known each other\Nsince we were kids, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective runt and the\Ndaughter of a police detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an ominous couple...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? How come? What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was acting as your big\Nsister and keeping watch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:11:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the creepy Tokyo girl\Nwon't try and seduce you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keeping watch? From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Tsutenkaku Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I see! She was the\None I sensed watching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...attitude?! I was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!\NYou should've joined us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm just here to show you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where to next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess only Osaka Castle is left...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! Take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to this man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know! He suddenly\Nfell onto the hood of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the roof of this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone's up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakata-han! Contact the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Heiji!\N- Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now you tell us why you dropped\Nthat body on top of a police car!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! I'm just a!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! He was called to the roof?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Someone called this guy\Nabout a strange man on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:13:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I run a tea shop on the second floor, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what sent the body falling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body was wrapped in rope,\Nattached to the roof's handrail,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and covered with a tarp, while\Nthe other end of the rope
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was tied to the door so the rope\Nwould come undone when opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I put his estimated time of\Ndeath at about one full day ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So someone murdered him this\Ntime yesterday and left him hanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why on top of a police car?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably just coincidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it could be someone\Ntrying to make an example...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Example?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The knife through the wallet and heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is clearly connected\Nwith those incidents...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Lady! Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There she goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I got her license plate number.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But never mind that. Tell me\Nabout "those incidents," Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serial murders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Tojiri Police Station, Osaka"\NSerial murders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serial murders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that man who fell was the third one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In each case, they were stabbed\Nin the chest, through their wallets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After they were strangled\Nto death with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was someone who\Nheld a grudge about money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we can't say that for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Nagao Hidetoshi\NConvenience store owner"\NThe first victim, Nagao Hidetoshi,\Nwas a convenience store owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first victim, Nagao Hidetoshi,\Nwas a convenience store owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Nishiguchi Tayo\NPub mistress"\NThe next victim, Nishiguchi Tayo,\Nwas the mistress of a small pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Nishiguchi Tayo\NPub mistress"\NAnd the one who fell was\NNoyasu Kazuto, a taxi driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the one who fell was\NNoyasu Kazuto, a taxi driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Noyasu Kazuto\NTaxi driver"\NAnd the one who fell was\NNoyasu Kazuto, a taxi driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of them had enough money\Nto incur someone's wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, none of them\Nare connected in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were all born, raised,\Nschooled, and employed in Osaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but all in different places.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found it, Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!\NWe found a link between the victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Goshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Any comments?!\N- Goshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't this from Goshi Sotaro's\Ncorruption case six years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case where his secretary took\Nresponsibility for him and quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I recall, the secretary's name was Nagao...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is our Nagao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagao Hidetoshi, the first one who was killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But didn't you already\Ninvestigate this? Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, take a look at the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's Noyasu, the third victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he was Assemblyman\NGoshi's driver until four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His former secretary and his former driver...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assemblyman Goshi may be involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought so too, so one of my\Nseniors is headed to his place now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, he's famous for his hatred of police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just going to see him won't help anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what do you say we\Npay a visit too, Sakata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on! You should leave that to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't just let the guy who\Nscrewed up your Osaka tour get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Head over to my house!\NKazuha can tell you where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji! Do you have the good luck charm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, sure do. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What good luck charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:17:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A good luck charm I gave him.\NIt's always protected his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last time he forgot it, he\Ngot really hurt in a kendo match!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're very important charms!\NThere are only two in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, remember that story\Nabout us and the handcuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I secretly put a piece of the\Nchain in his good luck charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though it's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind that. I don't\Nsee the runt anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Eh?!\N- Did he go to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess this means no more police cars...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sakata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You gotta write a letter apologizing\Nfor the crushed car, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what's with the gut?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kid'll be helpful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But won't Mori-han be worried?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay! I'll call him later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me, we used\Nthe license plate number to get
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the address and phone number\Nof that suspicious woman you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her name is Okazaki Sumie, age 39.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She divorced last year and lives\Nalone in the West Side Apartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to check her out first?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It seemed like she knew something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll call to see if she's home or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"West Side Apartments"\NHere, I'll call to see if she's home or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"West Side Apartments"\NAt 1:00 pm today, a body\Nfell near the Shinsai Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 1:00 pm today, a body\Nfell near the Shinsai Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased was identified\Nas Noyasu Kazuto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 41.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me... Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is this Okazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Sakata, I'm with\Nthe Tojiri Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Officer! Hurry here and protect me!\NI'm going to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything!\NJust hurry here! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just calm down! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lock your door and don't let anyone in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! We passed the West Side Apartments!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?! It's a one-way road\Nand it's a heavy traffic day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll take forever to turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be faster on foot! Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Watch it!\N- Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"West Side Apartments"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:20:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Lady! We're with that\Ncop who called earlier! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unlocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lady! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Sakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Okazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} isn't home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope. The place is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's crazy! I told her not to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did she contact you at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not. I didn't give her my number.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, hurry here. Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just got off the one-way road,\Nso I'll be there in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's from downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The public restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me she!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too late. She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?! Why did she go outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's a knife\Nthrough her wallet and chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's doing this?! And why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to do something else\Ndangerous, like stand on ice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also want to realize\Nthe dreams I came up with
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forever my destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a spaceship landed\Nright before my very eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I would leave my\Nfriends behind and leave Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said having uneventful\Nday after day is the best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I'm really Just running away,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.53,0:22:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,unable to keep up with days without you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like standing on ice, it's a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.81,0:22:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I loved you, my heart would\Nfly off even faster than light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forever my destiny
